Learn More






Visibility to Product Cost Maximizes Profitability



Networking with the World’s Foremost PCM Experts
including more than 20 of aPriori’s Product Managers, Professional Services Consultants and more than 100 of your peers from industry leaders in Aerospace & Defense, Automotive, Industrial Machinery, Consumer Durables and High Tech Electronics martkets.


Practical Workshops
This conference will offer more than 20 highly practical workshops dedicated to helping you improve your product cost management and product profitability practices the moment you return to your office. Presenters and Workshop leaders will include aPriori Product Managers, Business Consultants and Implementation/Technology Engineers plus an array of Subject Matter Experts from other leading Software Technology firms, Global Consulting Firms, Industry Analysts and University program leaders.





Keynote Presentations on Hot Topics in Manufacturing
Advanced Materials, New Manufacturing Technologies, Industrial Internet of Things, the rise of Simulation in the earliest design stages. COST INSIGHT 2017 will include several key speakers that will educate our audience on the latest trends that should be on your radar.


Insightful Case Studies
Past Case Study headliners have included Honeywell Aerospace, General Electric, Whirlpool, American Axle & Manufacturing, ThyssenKrupp and Celestica. Check back regularly for announcements as new Case Studies are added to this year’s agenda.







