Company Description


aPriori Technologies, Inc. develops and markets product cost management software. It offers aPriori Product Cost Management software platform, a software solution that provides real-time product cost assessments throughout the development and production process for engineers, sourcing and supply chain, cost experts and analysts, and suppliers. The firm also provides strategic value assessments, education services, and customer service and technical support. The company was founded by Michael L. Philpott, R. Sebastian Schrader and Eric Arno Hiller in 2003 and is headquartered in Concord, MA.




