Jobs (0)








Über uns

aPriori is a software company located in Concord, Massachusetts 
that develops and markets product cost management software. The company 
was founded in 2003. Since then, we have invested 150 man-years of 
development into our product and acquired numerous world class 
manufacturing corporations as customers. Launch New Products at or Below Target Cost
Even best-in-class manufacturing companies can miss their cost 
targets when launching new products. With aPriori, engineers can explore
 more design alternatives earlier in the development process without 
sacrificing schedules. Within seconds of making a design change, aPriori
 provides a real-time assessment of how the change has affected the cost
 of the part or product. With access to real-time product cost 
information, engineers make better decisions that prevent costs from 
being designed into new products while reducing the need for changes 
later in development – when making changes is incrementally more 
expensive. 
Never Overpay for Outsourced Parts
aPriori makes it possible for companies to ensure consistently 
optimal pricing for their outsourced parts and products. With aPriori’s 
real-time product cost information, sourcing professionals always know 
precisely how much a part or product “should cost” to produce. Access to
 precise “should cost” information enables sourcing experts to easily 
identify where they are overpaying for outsourced parts and to always 
negotiate the best deals with suppliers. The result is significant 
product cost savings en route to meeting (or surpassing) cost reduction 
goals. 
Maximize Cost Savings on Re-Design Work
For re-design projects, aPriori provides design engineers with 
instant cost feedback as they attempt to cost-reduce production parts. 
Designers can simply load parts to see what they cost today and then 
evaluate cost-saving, alternative designs using aPriori’s precise 
product cost information. Cost assessments are delivered in real-time as
 designs are modified, providing engineers with instant visibility into 
how the most recent change will impact overall cost. With aPriori, 
designers always know what it “should cost” to produce a design without 
having to wait for a formal cost estimate or supplier quote. As a 
result, engineers can evaluate more alternatives and make better 
decisions that ultimately result in lower product costs. 
Increase the Accuracy and Speed of RFQ Responses
OEMs are looking to outsource business to suppliers, but demand 
accurate and detailed quotations. From the supplier’s perspective, it’s 
challenging to keep up with the number of business opportunities because
 generating accurate and detailed quotations is a manual, 
resource-intensive process. With aPriori, the time required to generate a
 detailed cost estimate can be reduced from days to minutes. Interested to learn more about aPriori?Please feel free to contact us or to visit our youtube.com channel and follow us on twitter.com to watch product demos and case studdies and stay up- to date about the newest information regarding aPriori.Interested in a career at aPriori?We are always looking for talented and motivated individuals to join our team. Please have a look here!

